09-10 January Yellow Cream for Cream Puffs or Cannoli

- 1/2 cup sugar
- 1/3 cup cornstarch 
- 1/2 teaspoon salt
- 2   cups milk
- 4   egg yolks, slightly beaten
- 2   teaspoon butter
- 1   teaspoon vanilla

Mix sugar, cornstarch, and salt. Stir in milk and cook, stirring constantly until the mixture thickens. Remove from heat, add 1/2 of the egg mixture to pudding and stir. Then add rest of egg yolk. Return to heat and boil for 1 minute, stirring constantly. Remove from heat, blend in butter and vanilla. Cool before using.


Notes 
Add egg yolks to dry mix
Add warm milk to make a paste 
Add remaining milk cook for 4 min in microwave stirring every minute